WEBVTT

00:04:59.517 --> 00:05:02.122
I lost my best friend,

00:05:02.146 --> 00:05:04.099
I lost my whole world.

00:05:05.784 --> 00:05:08.527
Shalon's daughter lost her mother

00:05:08.551 --> 00:05:11.237
and all of the relationship possibilities

00:05:11.261 --> 00:05:14.065
that could have existed
between the two of them.

00:05:16.362 --> 00:05:19.273
The society may have suffered
the greater loss.

00:05:20.752 --> 00:05:23.030
Who knows how many medical advancements

00:05:23.054 --> 00:05:27.518
or social-justice contributions
Shalon may have made

00:05:27.542 --> 00:05:31.707
if only her medical provider
had listened to her